<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/login.css' />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <title>Registruj se</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container" id="container">
    <div class="form-container log-in-container">
        <form action="/register/new-user" method="post" class="login-box" autocomplete="on">
            <h1>Registruj se</h1>
            <input type="text" name="type" placeholder="Tip korisnika">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Ime">
            <input type="text" name="lastname" placeholder="Prezime">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Korisničko ime" />
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Lozinka" />
            <input type="text" name="study_program" placeholder="Studijski program"/>
            <button type="submit">Kreiraj</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay-container">
        <div class="overlay">
            <div class="overlay-panel overlay-right">
                <h1>eStudent</h1>
                <p>Dobro došli na mjesto namjenjeno za sve studente, koji žele sticati nova znanja, a pri tome imati sve na jednom mjestu.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>